-- The `Structural` predicate: "no `Agen` subterm anywhere".

data Structural : ‚àÄ {A B} ‚Üí HomTerm A B ‚Üí Set where
  structural-id : ‚àÄ {A} ‚Üí Structural (id {A})
  structural-Œª‚áí : ‚àÄ {A} ‚Üí Structural (Œª‚áí {A})
  structural-Œª‚áê : ‚àÄ {A} ‚Üí Structural (Œª‚áê {A})
  structural-œÅ‚áí : ‚àÄ {A} ‚Üí Structural (œÅ‚áí {A})
  structural-œÅ‚áê : ‚àÄ {A} ‚Üí Structural (œÅ‚áê {A})
  structural-Œ±‚áí : ‚àÄ {A B C} ‚Üí Structural (Œ±‚áí {A} {B} {C})
  structural-Œ±‚áê : ‚àÄ {A B C} ‚Üí Structural (Œ±‚áê {A} {B} {C})
  structural-œÉ  : ‚àÄ {A B} ‚¶É s : Symm ‚â§ Symm ‚¶Ñ
                ‚Üí Structural (œÉ {A = A} {B = B} ‚¶É s ‚¶Ñ)
  structural-‚àò  : ‚àÄ {A B C} {h : HomTerm B C} {k : HomTerm A B}
                ‚Üí Structural h ‚Üí Structural k
                ‚Üí Structural (h ‚àò k)
  structural-‚äó  : ‚àÄ {A B C D} {h : HomTerm A B} {k : HomTerm C D}
                ‚Üí Structural h ‚Üí Structural k
                ‚Üí Structural (h ‚äó‚ÇÅ k)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- `NoSigma`: predicate "no `œÉ` subterm anywhere".  Strictly stronger
-- than `Structural` (which allows œÉ); morphisms satisfying `NoSigma`
-- live in the Mac Lane fragment, where coherence is fully constructive
-- via `Categories.MonoidalCoherence.Solver.solveM`.

data NoSigma : ‚àÄ {A B} ‚Üí HomTerm A B ‚Üí Set where
  nosigma-id : ‚àÄ {A} ‚Üí NoSigma (id {A})
  nosigma-Œª‚áí : ‚àÄ {A} ‚Üí NoSigma (Œª‚áí {A})
  nosigma-Œª‚áê : ‚àÄ {A} ‚Üí NoSigma (Œª‚áê {A})
  nosigma-œÅ‚áí : ‚àÄ {A} ‚Üí NoSigma (œÅ‚áí {A})
  nosigma-œÅ‚áê : ‚àÄ {A} ‚Üí NoSigma (œÅ‚áê {A})
  nosigma-Œ±‚áí : ‚àÄ {A B C} ‚Üí NoSigma (Œ±‚áí {A} {B} {C})
  nosigma-Œ±‚áê : ‚àÄ {A B C} ‚Üí NoSigma (Œ±‚áê {A} {B} {C})
  nosigma-‚àò  : ‚àÄ {A B C} {h : HomTerm B C} {k : HomTerm A B}
             ‚Üí NoSigma h ‚Üí NoSigma k
             ‚Üí NoSigma (h ‚àò k)
  nosigma-‚äó  : ‚àÄ {A B C D} {h : HomTerm A B} {k : HomTerm C D}
             ‚Üí NoSigma h ‚Üí NoSigma k
             ‚Üí NoSigma (h ‚äó‚ÇÅ k)

NoSigma‚ÜíStructural : ‚àÄ {A B} {f : HomTerm A B} ‚Üí NoSigma f ‚Üí Structural f
NoSigma‚ÜíStructural nosigma-id      = structural-id
NoSigma‚ÜíStructural nosigma-Œª‚áí      = structural-Œª‚áí
NoSigma‚ÜíStructural nosigma-Œª‚áê      = structural-Œª‚áê
NoSigma‚ÜíStructural nosigma-œÅ‚áí      = structural-œÅ‚áí
NoSigma‚ÜíStructural nosigma-œÅ‚áê      = structural-œÅ‚áê
NoSigma‚ÜíStructural nosigma-Œ±‚áí      = structural-Œ±‚áí
NoSigma‚ÜíStructural nosigma-Œ±‚áê      = structural-Œ±‚áê
NoSigma‚ÜíStructural (nosigma-‚àò h k) = structural-‚àò (NoSigma‚ÜíStructural h)
                                                   (NoSigma‚ÜíStructural k)
NoSigma‚ÜíStructural (nosigma-‚äó h k) = structural-‚äó (NoSigma‚ÜíStructural h)
                                                   (NoSigma‚ÜíStructural k)

-- Decide whether a structural term contains at least one `œÉ`.
HasSigma? : ‚àÄ {A B} {f : HomTerm A B} ‚Üí Structural f ‚Üí NoSigma f ‚äé ‚ä§
HasSigma? structural-id        = inj‚ÇÅ nosigma-id
HasSigma? structural-Œª‚áí        = inj‚ÇÅ nosigma-Œª‚áí
HasSigma? structural-Œª‚áê        = inj‚ÇÅ nosigma-Œª‚áê
HasSigma? structural-œÅ‚áí        = inj‚ÇÅ nosigma-œÅ‚áí
HasSigma? structural-œÅ‚áê        = inj‚ÇÅ nosigma-œÅ‚áê
HasSigma? structural-Œ±‚áí        = inj‚ÇÅ nosigma-Œ±‚áí
HasSigma? structural-Œ±‚áê        = inj‚ÇÅ nosigma-Œ±‚áê
HasSigma? structural-œÉ         = inj‚ÇÇ tt
HasSigma? (structural-‚àò sh sk) with HasSigma? sh | HasSigma? sk
... | inj‚ÇÅ nh | inj‚ÇÅ nk = inj‚ÇÅ (nosigma-‚àò nh nk)
... | _       | _       = inj‚ÇÇ tt
HasSigma? (structural-‚äó sh sk) with HasSigma? sh | HasSigma? sk
... | inj‚ÇÅ nh | inj‚ÇÅ nk = inj‚ÇÅ (nosigma-‚äó nh nk)
... | _       | _       = inj‚ÇÇ tt

