-- Atomic structural constructors are structural.  (The `Agen` atomic
-- constructor is excluded ‚Äî it has `nE ‚â° 1` and is handled separately.)

Atomic-non-Agen‚ÜíStructural
  : ‚àÄ {A B} {f : HomTerm A B}
  ‚Üí Atomic f ‚Üí nE ‚ü™ f ‚ü´ ‚â° 0 ‚Üí Structural f
Atomic-non-Agen‚ÜíStructural (atomic-Agen _)   ()
Atomic-non-Agen‚ÜíStructural atomic-id         _ = structural-id
Atomic-non-Agen‚ÜíStructural atomic-Œª‚áí         _ = structural-Œª‚áí
Atomic-non-Agen‚ÜíStructural atomic-Œª‚áê         _ = structural-Œª‚áê
Atomic-non-Agen‚ÜíStructural atomic-œÅ‚áí         _ = structural-œÅ‚áí
Atomic-non-Agen‚ÜíStructural atomic-œÅ‚áê         _ = structural-œÅ‚áê
Atomic-non-Agen‚ÜíStructural atomic-Œ±‚áí         _ = structural-Œ±‚áí
Atomic-non-Agen‚ÜíStructural atomic-Œ±‚áê         _ = structural-Œ±‚áê
Atomic-non-Agen‚ÜíStructural (atomic-œÉ ‚¶É s ‚¶Ñ)  _ = structural-œÉ ‚¶É s ‚¶Ñ

